race.comment: KATTEGAT (3) will be fitter and has been racing in much tougher company. Will race forward from a low gate and flies third-up. Finds the right race. TURNAQUID (8)  just missed last time when a head away in second at Berrigan over 1100m. Has never gone better and is one of the main chances. NEPELA (1) was well beaten in the same race, but started a $2.60 favourite and will be better for the outing. In well with the 2kg claim. MIGHTY FEAT (4) resumes and is proven fresh. Was flat in stronger at his last two, but the form prior reads well. Jumps from a low gate with Parish aboard. LEGENDARY DIVA (10) dropped out last time but has been threatening prior. She also deserves consideration.
